rows.label: qst701005_msg0001
rows.name: Hawa-wa-wa, everyone! Why are you here?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0002
rows.name:
You're not here to explore the
neck of Gula as well... are you?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0003
rows.name:
I wish we were, but this time,
there are circumstances.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0004
rows.name: Laura, let's not be roundabout.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0005
rows.name:
I'll be blunt. Can you
lend us your strength? We
can't do it on our own.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0006
rows.name: M-Me??

rows.label: qst701005_msg0007
rows.name:
Hah... could it be an invitation
to participate in a spicy
food eating contest!?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0008
rows.name:
Hahaha... That sounds like
a contest from hell.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0009
rows.name:
If something like that really
existed, Adel would run away
before I could even invite him.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0010
rows.name: It's not? Then what could it be?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0011
rows.name:
...It seems there are
complicated circumstances.
Could you tell us the story?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0012
rows.name:
M-My father said that? I'm sorry
you had to go through that...

rows.label: qst701005_msg0013
rows.name:
No, it's fine. I understand
what he's trying to say.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0014
rows.name:
According to the handyman Dio,
he's on edge because he's worried
about his only daughter.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0015
rows.name:
Hmm, you think so? Even if that's
the case, would he get that angry?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0016
rows.name:
You told me before that your father
is as solid as Zain's Waytree.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0017
rows.name:
Yes... He's calm and quiet...
For him to suddenly say
something like that...

rows.label: qst701005_msg0018
rows.name:
According to what you said earlier, the
capital is still being targeted by a Blade
named Metsu. Could that be related?

rows.label: qst701005_msg0019
rows.name:
...Kaede-chan, I need your
advice. We're in the middle
of training, but I...

rows.label: qst701005_msg0020
rows.name:
You will return, won't
you? To the capital.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0021
rows.name:
It is natural to worry about
one's family. There is no
reason to oppose it.

rows.label: qst701005_msg0022
rows.name:
Ehehe, thank you! I
love you, Kaede-chan!

rows.label: qst701005_msg0023
rows.name:
Well then, everyone, let's
head for the capital!
